data.title: Vincent J. Cardinal
data.meta_description: Cardinal has directed EVERY BRILLIANT THING and THE FOREIGNER at the Utah Shakespeare Festival, LOVE BOAT stars Fred Grandy and Ted Lange in IM NOT RAPPAPORT, ON GOLDEN POND, MAX EMERSON of @Maxisms in THE LITTLE DOG LAUGHED, NOISES OFF, Pat Sajak in THE ODD COUPLE, Jerry Adler & Richard Kline
